  <identification>
    <creator type="composer">Words: Ludwig Helmbold (1532-1598). Translated by William M. Czamanske, 1939.
Music: 'Herr Jesu Christ, Dict Zu Uns Wend' from Cantionale Germanicum, Dresden, 1628.
Setting: "Mehrstimmiges ChoralBuch", 1906.
copyright: public domain.  This score is a part of the Open Hymnal Project, 2006 Revision.</creator>
