      <encoder>abc2xml version 268</encoder>
      <software>https://wim.vree.org/svgParse/abc2xml.html</software>
      <encoding-date>2026-07-21</encoding-date>
    </encoding>
    <source>Note that Concordia Publishing House, the original publisher of this translation
(in "The Lutheran Hymnal", 1941), published "Lutheran Worship" in 1982. This translation is not present in
the copyright notices, indicating that it had been released into the public domain.
Music source: "Mehrstimmiges ChoralBuch", 1906 Hymn #74, pdf page 69 Ed. Karl Brauer.</source>
